# @plurnk/plurnk-mimetypes — environment
# Family-prefix convention: every mimetypes-family knob is PLURNK_MIMETYPES_*.

# Root directory holding the side-by-side @plurnk/plurnk-mimetypes-grammar-*
# repos, used by the grammar maintenance scripts (grammars:check /
# grammars:update / grammars:publish). Defaults to this checkout's parent
# (the usual layout where every plurnk repo is cloned side by side).
#
# PLURNK_MIMETYPES_GRAMMARS_ROOT=..

# Root directory holding the side-by-side @plurnk/plurnk-mimetypes-* repos,
# scanned by deps:check (first-party exact-pin freshness + per-package npm audit).
# Defaults to this checkout's parent — same layout as PLURNK_MIMETYPES_GRAMMARS_ROOT.
#
# PLURNK_MIMETYPES_FAMILY_ROOT=..

# Minimum npm-audit severity deps:check flags (info|low|moderate|high|critical).
# Defaults to moderate.
#
# PLURNK_MIMETYPES_AUDIT_LEVEL=moderate

# PLURNK_MIMETYPES_NO_EMBED — comma-separated basename patterns naming content
# that should never be semantically derived (ProcessResult.noEmbed carries the
# matched pattern; consumers skip embedding → zero vectors + FTS-only). An
# entry without `/` matches the BASENAME; with `/` it matches the FULL PATH
# (directory drawers — hashed bundle names defeat basename rules). `*` is a
# wildcard and crosses `/`; an entry without `*` is exact. THIS LIST IS THE
# CLASSIFICATION — tune it per deployment; there is no code fallback and no
# hidden heuristic (unset/empty = nothing suppressed). Sane default:
PLURNK_MIMETYPES_NO_EMBED=*.min.*,*.map,package-lock.json,npm-shrinkwrap.json,packages.lock.json,yarn.lock,pnpm-lock.yaml,bun.lockb,Cargo.lock,poetry.lock,uv.lock,Pipfile.lock,Gemfile.lock,composer.lock,go.sum,flake.lock,gradle.lockfile,*/dist/*,dist/*,*/build/*,build/*,*/.next/*,.next/*,*/node_modules/*,node_modules/*
